K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468a-0: @468a / /bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal rnon po la bstod pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468a-1: mthing nag mdzes pas 'jam par 'tsher ba'i dbu //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468a-2: lcang lo rdzings bskyod mthing gi mtsho ltar g-yo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468a-3: dge ba'i spyi gtsug mtshan mchog g-yas su 'khyil //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-0: gtsug tor 'phags pas @468b skye bos bltar mi mthong //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-1: srid pa'i sdug bsngal ma lus gzhom pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-2: mthu chen byin gyis rgal ba gzhom pa'i phyir //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-3: dbu rgyan cod pan rgyal ba'i mchog gsang zhing //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-4: chos kyi rgyal thabs dbang gi pha rol phyin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-5: rin chen spug dang autpal 'dra ba yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-6: shin tu dvangs par dkar nag phyed pa'i spyan //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-7: smin tshugs mdzes pas zla ba tshes ltar 'khyug /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-8: mig 'dzums zur gyis lta bas byams pa'i rtags //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-9: sil snyan rnam dag mtshan rab 'bru chags pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-10: rin chen ma lus rnam pa du mas spras //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-11: rgyal ba'i zhing mang rnam pa sna tshogs su //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-12: rnam thar dpag yas chos sgo grangs med gnas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-13: shangs kyi dbyibs legs skye bo yongs las 'phags //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-14: mtho la yid tsam zur la legs pa'i mtshan //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-15: drang la chu phran 'dra bar mdzes pa'i tshul //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-16: bzang legs bskal pa brgyar yang bltar mi ngoms //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-17: padma le brgan tshon ltar dmar ba'i sgros //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-18: yid gzhungs 'phel ba 'khyil ba bzad legs sku //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-19: mdog sdug chu skyes snang ba mtsho lo bzhin //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-20: shin tu dang ba'i yid kyis 'dzum pa mdzad //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-21: zhal ras zla 'dra gser gyi mdog gis rgyas //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-22: 'od kyi dkyil 'khor gser phreng du mas spras //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-23: gsal ba'i 'od phung nyi ma brgya bas lhag /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:468b-24: 'od zer sna tshogs sprin phung bzhin du 'phro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-1: pa'i dbyangs kyi sgra sgrags pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-2: ka la ping ka lta bur yid 'phrog mdzad //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-3: sang sang dbyangs rab gsung dbyangs rab sgrags pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-4: seng+ge'i nga ro gser gyi dril ltar 'khrol //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-5: skyes mchog mdzad pa sgom par mdzad pa'i sku //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-6: cha lugs bzhin 'chang gzi brjid 'phags pa'i sku //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-7: gzhon nu'i tshul chags shin tu gzhon par gda'//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-8: gdul bya'i skye bo gzhon nu gzugs kyis gdul //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-9: dbu rgyan rin chen rnam pa sna tshogs dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-10: mu tig do shal gser gyi rgyan du bkod //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-11: padma lha yin bza' sil ma bsnams //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-12: g-yas na mtshon mchog bsnams pa thabs kyis 'dul //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-13: dpe med rno ba shes rab nyid du nges //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-14: chos dbyings tshul nyid yang dag brjod pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-15: mi shigs rdo rje gtan nas 'bigs pa'i tshul //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-16: g-yon pa shes rab pha rol phyin pa dang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-17: blang dor gnyis med bsam gyis mi khyab dbyings //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-18: zab mo'i chos nyid thugs su chud pa'i don //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-088-024:469a-19: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jam dpal rnon po la bstod pa rdzogs so //
